{"word":"G1351 - δίλογος - dílogos - dil'-og-os - Double-tongued","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">δίλογος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">dílogos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">dil'-og-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Double-tongued</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"இரு நாக்குள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"saying the same thing twice, repeating, double - tongued"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1364 - δίς - dís - dece/1364\">G1364</a> and <a href=\"#/G3056 - λόγος - lógos - log'-os/3056\">G3056</a>; <i>equivocal</i>, that is, telling a different story: - double-tongued.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}